ic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566580/extras/e8af033558ec05da329e790f2f4ce48f.poster.avif?t=1731576581\" width=128 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566580/extras/e8af033558ec05da329e790f2f4ce48f.webm?t=1731576581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566580/extras/e8af033558ec05da329e790f2f4ce48f.mp4?t=1731576581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The steps to pass the level are hidden in the cheats, and you can get tips.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566580/extras/f57d0eda3ae799a67525b20b3f6e8698.avif?t=1731576581\" width=650 height=180 /></span><br><br>You can also display them directly into the game scene, just check them and then try the level again.<br>When your operation is different from the game guide, you will also be reminded by color<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566580/extras/1c6e60db635dbddadfe88bd3c82efa9f.avif?t=1731576581\" width=650 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>By clearing this game, you will become smarter!</strong></h2><br><strong>Story background</strong><br>A long time ago, there was a special knight in the kingdom. He was very smart and could defeat all enemies without using weapons. Unfortunately, the knight fell seriously ill and passed away. In order to commemorate him, the king began to select knights who could rival him, and Those who can pass the selection are called <strong>Knight without sword</strong>",
